Mutual Funds









                institutional
            





Gold Equities
The strategy seeks to achieve its investment objective by investing in gold and other precious metals as well as securities of companies, located throughout the world, that are engaged in exploring, mining or processing gold and other precious metals. The product follows a value approach to investing and the team will identify companies that are undervalued based on their judgment of relative value and growth potential.
L to R: Coille van Alphen, Victor Huwang, Ryan McIntyre, John Hathaway, Douglas Groh






team



John Hathaway, CFA



Douglas B. Groh



Ryan McIntyre, CFA



Coille Van Alphen, CFA




