less. This fee is retained by each Fund and is credited to paid in capital.     
Redemptions to which the fee applies include redemptions of shares resulting    
from an exchange made pursuant to the Exchange Privilege, as defined in the     
Trust's Prospectus dated March 1, 2004, as supplemented on June 17, 2004 and    

